- `withUserAgentSuffix()` - add SDK version to user agent
- `parseProviderOptions()` - validate provider-specific options with Zod
- `postJsonToApi()` - make JSON POST requests
- `combineHeaders()` - merge header objects
- `FetchFunction` - custom fetch type
- `Resolvable<T>` - value or function returning value

